1. Install ELFIN followings intructions in README.
2. Remove bin folder from ELFIN installation. 
   (e.g. "rm -r $HOME/ELFINvxx/bin"), where xx is the version of
   ELFIN.
3. Create a symbolic link to bin folder in your git repository folder.
   (e.g. "ln -s $HOME/ELFINvxx/bin /my/git/repo/path/to/ELFIN/MODULE2/bin")